### What to REMOVE (after verification)

#### 1. Remove Redundant Formatting in Commands
After migration, commands should use OutputContext. Remove:
- Direct println! in commands (except debug/error)
- Manual JSON serialization (use ctx.json())
- Direct color calls (use Theme)

#### 2. Remove Old Pattern:
```rust
