### Label Coloring Strategy
Labels get consistent colors via hash:
```rust
fn label_color(label: &str) -> Color {
    let hash = label.bytes().fold(0u8, |acc, b| acc.wrapping_add(b));
    LABEL_PALETTE[hash as usize % LABEL_PALETTE.len()]
}
```

